## Mathematica
```Mathematica
a[n_]:=CountDistinct[Table[PowerMod[x-1, 5, 5^(n-1)], {x, 1, 5^(n-1)}]]; Array[a, 13]
```
## Python
```Python
def A365104(n): return len({pow(x,5,5**n) for x in range(5**n)}) # _Chai Wah Wu_, Sep 17 2023
```
